程序包 org.texttechnology.parliament_browser_6_4.helper

类 StringHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.texttechnology.parliament_browser_6_4.helper.StringHelper
  • public class StringHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    The StringHelper class provides utility functions for string manipulation, including cleaning and replacing substrings based on predefined rules. It is designed to assist in processing strings that require specific formatting or cleaning operations commonly used throughout the application.
    作者:
    Giuseppe Abrami

      • replaceList

        public static java.lang.String replaceList​(java.lang.String sInput,
                                           java.lang.String[] replaceList)
        Replaces occurrences of each string in replaceList within the input string with an empty string, then cleans the resulting string by trimming and removing specific unwanted characters.
        参数:
        sInput - The input string to be processed.
        replaceList - An array of strings that should be replaced with an empty string in the input.
        返回:
        The cleaned and processed string.

      • clean

        public static java.lang.String clean​(java.lang.String sInput)
        Cleans the input string by trimming leading and trailing whitespace.
        参数:
        sInput - The input string to be cleaned.
        返回:
        The cleaned string with removed leading and trailing whitespace.
